00:34:14,186 --> 00:34:22,653
portfolio isn't ready for Epic or for Ubisoft or whatever, what are some avenues that

746
00:34:22,653 --> 00:34:30,100
people can pursue that exist now that may not have existed 15 years ago to help people

747
00:34:30,100 --> 00:34:31,581
find their way in?

748
00:34:33,938 --> 00:34:36,341
We can't talk a little bit about it.

